{"tid":828571,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"返緊工既你，仲抽唔抽到時間做運動？","createTime":"2018-09-19T19:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T02:17:17.000Z","uid":86789,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea90bf9e940b79b83f2f39a0ca9db556144d937","tid":828571,"uid":86789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"小弟自從返文職開始少左走動<br />\nP.s. 以前返服務業一日都行到萬五至二萬步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於日前發現體重有上升趨勢<br />\n我想收工之後做下運動咁啦<br />\n利申唔鐘意跑步唔好叫我跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一諗到收工拎住個袋去街場打籃波真係好驚比人偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返得屋企啲街場都夠鐘鎖閘/熄燈<br />\n唉 咁落去唔係辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想keep fit啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5241be9d539f8af2126504369b186ee06f30c3","tid":828571,"uid":62277,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:47:52.000Z","msg":"放工連飯都唔想煮<br />\n做乜鳩運動吖"},{"pid":"e80f3b4c8ea0765fd79115a2a0bc884eb57cc8ad","tid":828571,"uid":193476,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T20:16:14.000Z","msg":"唔想咁辛苦，咪由得自己肥落去囉，肥又唔係犯法。"},{"pid":"1214a17330f8e07a964105e2e585e317ea3721af","tid":828571,"uid":177130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea90bf9e940b79b83f2f39a0ca9db556144d937","tid":828571,"uid":86789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"小弟自從返文職開始少左走動<br />\nP.s. 以前返服務業一日都行到萬五至二萬步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於日前發現體重有上升趨勢<br />\n我想收工之後做下運動咁啦<br />\n利申唔鐘意跑步唔好叫我跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一諗到收工拎住個袋去街場打籃波真係好驚比人偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返得屋企啲街場都夠鐘鎖閘/熄燈<br />\n唉 咁落去唔係辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想keep fit啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T20:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打泰拳，真心幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72412667c25add6c5c7f0cbb652c9f47af865969","tid":828571,"uid":177130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T20:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個星期唔使多，一兩日就到"},{"pid":"b202e5d22339f7624ae81cfe18a56a2aa67ddb82","tid":828571,"uid":100099,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T20:22:00.000Z","msg":"朝8晚6返6日<br />\n有5日都收工做運動<br />\n星期一三五 gym<br />\n星期二 跑街<br />\n星期四 打泰拳<br />\nkeep左半年<br />\n減左13kg"},{"pid":"555e7a648ff6e3b18d127a37f34463db655f7ce0","tid":828571,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b202e5d22339f7624ae81cfe18a56a2aa67ddb82","tid":828571,"uid":100099,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T20:22:00.000Z","msg":"朝8晚6返6日<br />\n有5日都收工做運動<br />\n星期一三五 gym<br />\n星期二 跑街<br />\n星期四 打泰拳<br />\nkeep左半年<br />\n減左13kg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T22:02:47.000Z","msg":"仲力做。。。"},{"pid":"303bdc8fa3cd5ee54282396b22ff0822ac3ca06f","tid":828571,"uid":33174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e80f3b4c8ea0765fd79115a2a0bc884eb57cc8ad","tid":828571,"uid":193476,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T20:16:14.000Z","msg":"唔想咁辛苦，咪由得自己肥落去囉，肥又唔係犯法。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T22:08:48.000Z","msg":"肥唔係犯法 係唔尊重自己 對自己人生放棄<br />\n連自己健康顧唔到仲點做其他野？"},{"pid":"648f885e40592437878817c3b2cfcca1600eb8b5","tid":828571,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T22:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{